query: SELECT e.id, e.gamePresenterId, DATE(e.evaluationDate) as eval_date, gp.name as gp_name, t.teamName, e.appearanceScore, e.gamePerformanceTotalScore FROM evaluations e LEFT JOIN game_presenters gp ON e.gamePresenterId = gp.id LEFT JOIN fm_teams t ON gp.teamId = t.id;
